data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom ranch in Oak Grove Meadows . Located in a cul-de-sac (great for the kiddos). BONUS room that could be a office, play-room, or even a 4th bedroom. Primary with a en-suite. New roof (2023) HVAC (2021). Kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. 400sqft (20x20) Detached garage with electricity on a 1/4 acre pie shape lot. Enjoy family time on Stamped concrete patio with a cobblestone fire pit . Chesapeake Arboretum is within close proximity. Located near the interstate , shopping , restaurants and the hospital.
